**Yes. Needed:**
> Option to launch a stream (and if possible vods) in the browser in popout mode so it's only the stream, no site, no chat. This is so browser adblock extensions work if wanted for a important stream.

- https://player.twitch.tv/?channel=STREAMER&enableExtensions=true&muted=false&parent=twitch.tv&player=popout&quality=auto&volume=1.0

